-Let's go.

114
00:10:18,084 --> 00:10:19,085
Go after them!

115
00:10:29,963 --> 00:10:31,798
Young master...

116
00:10:33,133 --> 00:10:35,068
-Yesha, quick...
-I thought I lost you.

117
00:10:35,135 --> 00:10:36,336
Quick.

118
00:10:36,970 --> 00:10:38,071
Be careful.

119
00:10:51,451 --> 00:10:52,552
Quick, Yesha.

120
00:10:54,554 --> 00:10:56,156
-Come in, quick...
-Come in here.

121
00:10:56,956 --> 00:10:58,992
Young master, I finally found you.

122
00:11:01,961 --> 00:11:04,464
-You...
-I'm warning you.

123
00:11:04,531 --> 00:11:06,866
Don't follow me. Do you hear me?

124
00:11:11,471 --> 00:11:12,839
Quick!

125
00:11:21,047 --> 00:11:23,349
Young master, don't run away!

126
00:11:23,416 --> 00:11:25,118
Young master, come back!

127
00:11:25,185 --> 00:11:27,554
What are you waiting for? Go get them.

128
00:11:27,620 --> 00:11:28,922
-Understood.
-Understood.

129
00:11:35,495 --> 00:11:37,497
You go that way. I'll go this way.

130
00:11:55,481 --> 00:11:56,516
Ah Xing.

131
00:11:58,351 --> 00:11:59,552
Ah Xing, what's wrong with you?

132
00:12:00,153 --> 00:12:01,221
Is this the right room?

133
00:12:41,194 --> 00:12:42,328
Young master.

134
00:12:43,229 --> 00:12:44,764
Young master, you come back.

135
00:12:45,665 --> 00:12:47,834
Young master, what's wrong with you?

136
00:12:47,934 --> 00:12:50,637
You don't recognize me?

137
00:12:50,803 --> 00:12:52,472
You don't even recognize me.

138
00:12:52,538 --> 00:12:53,940
I'm Aunt Yu.

139
00:12:56,242 --> 00:12:57,477
Only eight minutes left.

140
00:12:58,978 --> 00:13:00,146
Young master.

141
00:13:00,380 --> 00:13:01,514
Don't be afraid.

142
00:13:02,181 --> 00:13:04,951
It's me, Aunt Yu, who raised you up.

143
00:13:05,018 --> 00:13:07,253
How can I harm you?

144
00:13:10,089 --> 00:13:11,090
Take them down.

145
00:13:12,925 --> 00:13:14,060
What are you doing?

146
00:13:14,127 --> 00:13:16,896
The madam told us to keep you here.
Don't make this harder.

147
00:13:25,738 --> 00:13:26,839
Quick, go.

148
00:13:26,906 --> 00:13:28,741
Young master, don't leave me.

149
00:13:38,217 --> 00:13:39,419
Young master, come back.

150
00:13:40,286 --> 00:13:41,954
-Young master.
-Get out of my way.

151
00:13:42,388 --> 00:13:43,389
Young master.

152
00:13:45,925 --> 00:13:46,926
Follow me.

153
00:13:48,561 --> 00:13:49,662
Young master.

154
00:13:54,634 --> 00:13:55,735
Go.

155
00:14:00,039 --> 00:14:01,140
Watch out, Aunt Yu.

156
00:14:09,349 --> 00:14:11,150
Ma'am, the young master...

157
00:14:11,351 --> 00:14:13,219
He... is gone.

158
00:14:13,986 --> 00:14:15,321
You useless people!

159
00:14:16,389 --> 00:14:17,323
Keep searching.

160
00:14:17,824 --> 00:14:19,792
Inside and outside the house.

161
00:14:19,992 --> 00:14:21,828
Find them no matter what.

162
00:14:22,161 --> 00:14:23,262
Yes, ma'am.

163
00:14:23,329 --> 00:14:25,398
You, go that way. You two, go that way.

164
00:14:25,465 --> 00:14:26,966
You two, follow me.

165
00:14:49,021 --> 00:14:51,290
The gate must be heavily guarded.

166
00:14:51,357 --> 00:14:52,892
Don't fall into the trap.

167
00:14:53,092 --> 00:14:54,427
This is the only way.

168
00:14:55,428 --> 00:14:56,429
Now, go.

169
00:14:58,865 --> 00:14:59,866
Young master.

170
00:15:05,905 --> 00:15:07,874
Go.

171
00:15:38,838 --> 00:15:39,806
Ma'am.

172
00:15:40,039 --> 00:15:41,274
Where are they?

173
00:15:41,874 --> 00:15:43,009
Who?

174
00:15:44,010 --> 00:15:46,712
You mean the young master.
I heard he's back.

175
00:15:46,779 --> 00:15:48,781
I might saw him just now.

176
00:15:48,915 --> 00:15:50,483
I followed him and...

177
00:15:50,750 --> 00:15:52,285
he disappeared.

178
00:15:57,423 --> 00:15:58,591
You useless people!

179
00:15:58,925 --> 00:16:00,293
You can't even stop two people.

180
00:16:01,093 --> 00:16:02,595
Continue searching.

181
00:16:03,262 --> 00:16:04,864
You must find them.

182
00:16:05,731 --> 00:16:06,732
Understood.

183
00:16:35,561 --> 00:16:36,462
That was close.

184
00:16:39,532 --> 00:16:42,168
I know my family is rich,
but I don't know the house is that huge.

185
00:16:43,436 --> 00:16:45,605
I felt so cold in there.

186
00:16:45,838 --> 00:16:47,707
-Cold?
-Yes.

187
00:16:47,773 --> 00:16:49,041
Cold.

188
00:16:49,108 --> 00:16:50,810
Except around that granny.

189
00:16:51,344 --> 00:16:52,545
You mean Aunt Yu.

190
00:16:54,213 --> 00:16:55,214
Aunt Yu.

191
00:16:55,948 --> 00:16:57,250
Aunt Yu.

192
00:16:59,185 --> 00:17:01,220
Weird. She seems to be
a nice person to me,

193
00:17:01,287 --> 00:17:02,688
but why can't I remember anything?

194
00:17:03,022 --> 00:17:05,258
-Who is she?
-Leave it be.

195
00:17:06,192 --> 00:17:07,527
Now, we have the photo.

196
00:17:09,629 --> 00:17:11,497
They seem to be your classmates.

197
00:17:13,866 --> 00:17:15,601
We have new leads now.

198
00:17:16,369 --> 00:17:18,471
Your school and your classmates.

199
00:17:40,059 --> 00:17:42,395
Ah Si came back? Was he alone?

200
00:17:42,862 --> 00:17:44,931
No. There was a girl.

201
00:17:45,331 --> 00:17:46,365
I don't know her.

202
00:17:47,867 --> 00:17:49,235
Could it be another Zhongze?

203
00:17:50,736 --> 00:17:53,005
She doesn't look like a bad guy.

204
00:17:53,172 --> 00:17:54,707
She was helping our young master.

205
00:17:54,907 --> 00:17:56,275
She was kind to him.

206
00:17:56,375 --> 00:17:57,643
How kind?

207
00:17:58,678 --> 00:18:00,012
How kind?

208
00:18:00,112 --> 00:18:01,147
Well...

209
00:18:01,714 --> 00:18:02,782
Master Ximen.

210
00:18:02,848 --> 00:18:04,750
I... I'm not sure about that.

211
00:18:05,885 --> 00:18:07,119
No matter who she is,

212
00:18:07,820 --> 00:18:09,221
she's good if she treats Ah Si nicely.

213
00:18:12,525 --> 00:18:13,559
Aunt Yu.

214
00:18:13,726 --> 00:18:15,227
They just broke in,

215
00:18:15,294 --> 00:18:16,762
messed around,

216
00:18:16,829 --> 00:18:18,064
and left again?

217
00:18:18,164 --> 00:18:20,032
He was afraid of being caught by Madam.

218
00:18:20,099 --> 00:18:23,069
If he was caught again,
he'll be locked up.

219
00:18:24,303 --> 00:18:26,839
Is it like challenging the 18 Bronzemen?

220
00:18:28,174 --> 00:18:29,041
Yes.

221
00:18:29,742 --> 00:18:31,444
Ah Si is always full of surprise.

222
00:18:31,744 --> 00:18:32,912
No one can predict his next move.

223
00:18:34,747 --> 00:18:36,382
This is something Ah Si could do.

224
00:18:42,154 --> 00:18:44,457
Masters, I've been here for a long time.

225
00:18:44,523 --> 00:18:45,791
I have to get back now.

226
00:18:45,992 --> 00:18:48,361
I'll tell you if there's any news
about the young master.

227
00:18:49,028 --> 00:18:50,162
Thank you, Aunt Yu.

228
00:18:55,301 --> 00:18:56,502
What are you doing?

229
00:18:57,003 --> 00:18:58,270
I will tell Shancai about this.

230
