00:19:35,374 --> 00:19:36,575
She's not answering.

242
00:19:38,010 --> 00:19:42,048
It's weird. Shancai's phone
is either off or not answered.

243
00:19:46,552 --> 00:19:47,753
You, too?

244
00:19:49,155 --> 00:19:50,723
What is Shancai doing?

245
00:19:52,458 --> 00:19:53,793
I don't think she's doing anything.

246
00:19:54,260 --> 00:19:55,361
She's hiding.

247
00:19:56,662 --> 00:19:59,498
Doing or hiding. It's fine
as long as she doesn't lose her memory.

248
00:20:00,232 --> 00:20:02,134
We can just search the entire Taipei.

249
00:20:07,139 --> 00:20:08,174
Boss.

250
00:20:08,474 --> 00:20:09,675
This is Ximen.

251
00:20:10,142 --> 00:20:11,444
Is Shancai there?

252
00:20:15,981 --> 00:20:18,451
Could you please tell me
the other places she's working at?

253
00:20:32,698 --> 00:20:34,500
Aunt Yu, you're back.

254
00:20:38,170 --> 00:20:39,472
Ma... ma'am.

255
00:20:40,473 --> 00:20:42,007
Did you meet Ah Si?

256
00:20:45,144 --> 00:20:46,479
That's just what I thought.

257
00:20:46,812 --> 00:20:49,281
There are so many people in the house.

258
00:20:49,715 --> 00:20:52,818
Ah Si and that girl
don't have wings on them.

259
00:20:53,252 --> 00:20:55,421
How could they just disappear?

260
00:20:56,889 --> 00:20:57,923
Aunt Yu.

261
00:20:58,891 --> 00:21:01,527
Did you help them sneak out?

262
00:21:01,894 --> 00:21:03,763
No, ma'am.

263
00:21:03,896 --> 00:21:06,966
I met Master Ximen and Master Meizuo.

264
00:21:07,199 --> 00:21:09,535
I... I didn't meet our young master.

265
00:21:09,735 --> 00:21:11,771
I don't know who he's with.

266
00:21:11,837 --> 00:21:13,806
I don't know where he is now.

267
