Aunt Yu.

268
00:21:17,409 --> 00:21:19,512
At your age,

269
00:21:19,879 --> 00:21:22,248
your brain's not working very well.

270
00:21:23,916 --> 00:21:24,950
Ma'am.

271
00:21:25,151 --> 00:21:27,620
Are you bringing up my retirement again?

272
00:21:28,721 --> 00:21:30,422
I shouldn't have pitied you.

273
00:21:31,223 --> 00:21:33,259
You said you heard Ah Si was sick

274
00:21:33,659 --> 00:21:35,494
and you're too worried to sleep.

275
00:21:36,061 --> 00:21:37,897
You kept begging me,

276
00:21:38,564 --> 00:21:40,699
so I brought you back.

277
00:21:42,635 --> 00:21:47,640
But the person you are now
can't tell what's good and bad for Ah Si

278
00:21:48,407 --> 00:21:54,613
and can't be assigned to manage the house.

279
00:21:56,682 --> 00:22:00,085
Quit your job and enjoy your life,

280
00:22:01,387 --> 00:22:03,622
or it'll be a burden

281
00:22:05,057 --> 00:22:06,425
for the both of us.

282
00:22:08,527 --> 00:22:09,595
Ma'am.

283
00:22:10,262 --> 00:22:12,331
No one knows more
about this family than me.

284
00:22:13,499 --> 00:22:16,035
I'm not in charge of managing it.

285
00:22:17,636 --> 00:22:19,505
But our young master.

286
00:22:19,572 --> 00:22:22,975
Why did he have to sneak
into his own house?

287
00:22:23,275 --> 00:22:25,511
Why did he have to run away like that?

288
00:22:27,546 --> 00:22:30,182
The young master was raised by me.

289
00:22:30,916 --> 00:22:32,852
So, no matter what,

290
00:22:33,185 --> 00:22:35,087
even I'm too old to walk,

291
00:22:35,788 --> 00:22:37,790
I will protect the young master
to the end.

292
00:22:39,291 --> 00:22:40,492
Don't you remember?

293
00:22:41,126 --> 00:22:43,195
Ah Si doesn't remember you anymore,

294
00:22:45,097 --> 00:22:50,836
so your appearance in the house
has no influence on Ah Si.

295
00:22:52,671 --> 00:22:58,043
You've done a lot
for the Daoming family in decades.

296
00:22:58,811 --> 00:23:00,012
So...

297
00:23:00,613 --> 00:23:06,952
Don't sabotage your reputation
built by yourself at this age.

298
00:23:22,701 --> 00:23:25,738
Your things are packed up by Butler Liu.

299
00:23:27,339 --> 00:23:31,777
Just tell Butler Liu to send a car
to take you to your desired place.

300
00:23:55,601 --> 00:23:58,837
Please have a taste of our fruit wine.
Orange, strawberry, Hami melon flavors.

301
00:23:58,904 --> 00:23:59,972
It's delicious.

302
00:24:00,139 --> 00:24:02,141
Do you want to taste
our fruit wine, young lady?

303
00:24:02,474 --> 00:24:04,276
Please have a taste of our fruit wine.

304
00:24:05,344 --> 00:24:08,414
Please have a taste of our fruit wine.
Do you want to taste our fruit wine, sir?

305
00:24:21,226 --> 00:24:22,461
It tastes strange.

306
00:24:25,864 --> 00:24:27,132
But it's not bad.

307
00:24:28,133 --> 00:24:29,668
How do you know I'm here?

308
00:24:30,202 --> 00:24:31,837
We're here to sort you out.

309
00:24:32,271 --> 00:24:34,206
Shancai, some friend you are.

310
00:24:42,514 --> 00:24:44,083
Why are you wearing such an ugly costume?

311
00:24:44,483 --> 00:24:46,352
Sir, do you want to taste our fruit wine?

312
00:24:47,987 --> 00:24:49,188
Thank you.

313
00:24:50,022 --> 00:24:51,323
She said "thank you" to us.

314
00:24:51,390 --> 00:24:52,925
How should we scold her?

315
00:24:53,559 --> 00:24:55,627
Want to taste it? It's very delicious.

316
00:25:00,432 --> 00:25:01,500
Thank you.

317
00:25:07,673 --> 00:25:09,274
Want to drink some fruit tea, young lady?

318
00:25:09,341 --> 00:25:10,676
No, thank you.

319
00:25:13,879 --> 00:25:15,047
Hey, Shancai.

320
00:25:15,514 --> 00:25:18,017
Why are you exhausting yourself like that?

321
00:25:18,784 --> 00:25:20,152
I want to make some money.

322
00:25:20,352 --> 00:25:21,620
Besides paying my tuition,

323
00:25:22,321 --> 00:25:23,622
I...

324
00:25:26,125 --> 00:25:27,593
I'll tell it to you straight.

325
00:25:27,659 --> 00:25:30,162
Do you know
those large electronic billboards?

326
00:25:32,064 --> 00:25:34,633
I want to put on an ad to find Daoming Si.

327
00:25:34,967 --> 00:25:37,169
Of course, I won't expose his identity.

328
00:25:37,536 --> 00:25:41,073
However, it costs a lot to have such ad,
so I'm taking on one more job.

329
00:25:41,306 --> 00:25:43,442
Why didn't you tell us about this?

330
00:25:45,110 --> 00:25:47,379
Because you said it's stupid
to go high-profile.

331
00:25:47,446 --> 00:25:49,782
The more I think about it,
the more stupid I realize it is.

332
00:25:49,848 --> 00:25:52,918
I'm glad I didn't tell you that day,
or I would get scolded for shit.

333
00:25:53,585 --> 00:25:54,586
Really?

334
00:25:55,687 --> 00:25:58,023
I haven't seen a stinky snail before.

335
00:25:59,191 --> 00:26:00,726
Who are you implying a snail?

336
00:26:00,793 --> 00:26:03,195
I haven't scolded you yet.
What kind of message is that?

337
00:26:03,429 --> 00:26:04,997
How can snail go upside down
with its shell?

338
00:26:05,097 --> 00:26:06,598
You can carry me on your back and try it.

339
00:26:06,799 --> 00:26:08,300
I'm not gonna fall into your trap.

340
00:26:08,967 --> 00:26:10,536
If I stand upside down with you
on my back,

341
00:26:11,270 --> 00:26:12,838
I will be the snail.

342
00:27:33,352 --> 00:27:34,920
It's weird.

343
00:27:34,987 --> 00:27:37,022
He told me to come here
without showing up.

344
00:27:37,422 --> 00:27:39,258
What is Meizuo up to?

345
00:28:17,229 --> 00:28:20,299
HUMOR TIME

346
00:28:31,009 --> 00:28:35,013
AH SI, I'LL BE WAITING FOR YOU FOREVER

347
00:28:39,051 --> 00:28:42,654
AH SI, I'LL BE WAITING FOR YOU FOREVER
0917-595600

348
00:28:45,624 --> 00:28:49,728
Lei, Ximen, Meizuo, thank you.

349
00:28:50,162 --> 00:28:51,563
Thank you.

350
00:28:59,538 --> 00:29:04,309
AH SI, I'LL BE WAITING FOR YOU FOREVER

351
00:29:27,232 --> 00:29:30,736
AH SI, I'LL BE WAITING FOR YOU FOREVER
0917-595600

352
00:29:35,774 --> 00:29:37,676
-Hi.
-<i>Where are you?</i>

353
00:29:38,543 --> 00:29:40,846
-Who is this?
-<i>I'm Si.</i>

354
00:29:41,280 --> 00:29:43,849
-No, you're not.
-<i>Oh, I miss you so much.</i>

355
00:29:44,549 --> 00:29:46,218
Quit messing with me.
I'm waiting for a call.

356
00:29:50,188 --> 00:29:51,156
Hello.

357
00:29:51,723 --> 00:29:54,693
<i>My name is Ah Si, too. I can show you
my ID card if you don't believe me.</i>

358
00:29:54,926 --> 00:29:56,528
Sir, you're going too far.

359
00:29:57,262 --> 00:29:59,665
<i>Come on, making a friend
costs you nothing.</i>

360
00:30:00,766 --> 00:30:04,202
I'm begging you, okay? I'm waiting
for a very important phone call.

361
00:30:07,639 --> 00:30:10,075
I'm taking on two jobs,
working over ten hours every day

362
00:30:10,142 --> 00:30:11,777
just for this ad.

363
00:30:14,680 --> 00:30:17,516
He is missing and he might be in danger

364
00:30:17,716 --> 00:30:19,151
and all I can do is to wait.

365
00:30:19,985 --> 00:30:21,186
Waiting to hear his voice.

366
00:30:21,453 --> 00:30:24,823
Even what he looks like
when he is talking is getting blurry.

367
00:30:28,694 --> 00:30:32,097
I regret I didn't take more photos of him.

368
00:30:32,731 --> 00:30:34,833
I regret I didn't record him with V8.

369
00:30:36,335 --> 00:30:38,070
Do you know what is regret?

370
00:30:39,271 --> 00:30:40,605
Have you ever experienced it?

371
00:30:42,007 --> 00:30:43,375
Because if you have,

372
00:30:43,642 --> 00:30:47,346
I'm begging you to leave me alone,
and stop jamming the phone, okay?

373
00:31:02,160 --> 00:31:03,128
<i>Hello.</i>

374
00:31:03,662 --> 00:31:05,564
<i>Sorry, it's me again.</i>

375
00:31:05,964 --> 00:31:09,134
<i>I forget to tell you
that I hope you can find Si very soon.</i>

376
00:31:09,334 --> 00:31:10,369
<i>I'm rooting for you.</i>

377
00:31:17,275 --> 00:31:21,513
PAYPHONE

378
00:31:39,965 --> 00:31:40,966
Hello.

379
00:31:57,716 --> 00:32:00,018
Shan Cai, why didn't you answer
your phone?

380
00:32:01,686 --> 00:32:02,721
Did you see that?

381
00:32:04,823 --> 00:32:05,891
Thank you.

382
00:32:11,630 --> 00:32:12,631
Hello.

383
00:32:13,298 --> 00:32:14,933
<i>Do you want to know where Ah Si is?</i>

384
00:32:15,133 --> 00:32:16,468
<i>Come out and drink a cup of coffee.</i>

385
00:32:17,536 --> 00:32:18,737
Boring.

386
00:32:20,806 --> 00:32:21,907
What's wrong?

387
00:32:24,276 --> 00:32:25,377
Nothing.

388
00:32:27,646 --> 00:32:28,914
It's just...

389
00:32:29,214 --> 00:32:31,450
I've been answering
random calls all night.

390
00:32:38,990 --> 00:32:40,225
Didn't Ah Si call you?

391
00:32:42,327 --> 00:32:45,363
Everyone was claiming they were Ah Si.

392
00:32:55,040 --> 00:32:56,808
<i>Young lady, do you want a cup of coffee?</i>

393
00:32:56,875 --> 00:32:58,577
Great, where?

394
00:33:04,216 --> 00:33:05,283
Talk.

395
00:33:05,617 --> 00:33:07,719
-Meizuo.
-Why don't you talk?

396
00:33:08,253 --> 00:33:10,322
-What are you gonna do?
-Beat him up.

397
00:33:12,424 --> 00:33:13,458
Forget it.

398
00:33:16,495 --> 00:33:18,563
Hey, why did you turn off the phone?

399
00:33:18,964 --> 00:33:20,899
Do you want to get those harassing calls?

400
00:33:22,033 --> 00:33:23,835
What if Daoming Si calls me?

401
00:33:23,935 --> 00:33:26,705
<i>Your call will go to voicemail.</i>

402
00:33:26,771 --> 00:33:28,373
<i>We'll start charging after the "beep."</i>

403
00:33:28,440 --> 00:33:30,175
<i>Please hang up
if you won't leave a message.</i>

404
00:34:00,705 --> 00:34:01,740
Hello.

405
00:34:04,209 --> 00:34:05,310
<i>Hello.</i>

406
00:34:07,178 --> 00:34:08,547
<i>Hello. Talk.</i>

407
00:34:09,381 --> 00:34:10,682
You are Ah Si, right?

408
00:34:11,049 --> 00:34:12,884
I'm telling you, you boring sick bastard.

409
00:34:12,951 --> 00:34:14,686
I'll beat you up if you call again.

410
00:34:21,660 --> 00:34:23,762
Why are there so many boring people?

411
00:34:26,965 --> 00:34:27,999
Give it back.

412
00:34:31,002 --> 00:34:32,070
Shancai.

413
00:34:32,304 --> 00:34:34,139
Maybe this is not the right way.

414
00:34:35,640 --> 00:34:36,775
Give it back.

415
00:34:38,610 --> 00:34:40,111
Could you please see the reality?

416
00:34:47,819 --> 00:34:49,254
I like it, okay?

417
00:34:55,493 --> 00:34:57,162
This is my only hope now.

418
00:35:08,373 --> 00:35:11,209
I didn't get the person
but a bunch of problems.

419
00:35:12,844 --> 00:35:15,914
I should've left my phone number
and taught them a lesson.

420
00:35:17,115 --> 00:35:19,851
We hope Shancai could be the first one
to get Ah Si's call.

421
00:35:22,721 --> 00:35:24,055
Turn off the billboard.

422
00:35:25,123 --> 00:35:27,759
The more you hope,
the more disappointed you will be.

423
00:35:30,395 --> 00:35:32,097
I'm worried about another breakdown
of Shancai.

424
00:35:32,163 --> 00:35:36,434
Maybe after a few breakdowns,
she can accept the fact.

425
00:35:39,838 --> 00:35:42,340
Sometimes I really wonder
if you're from outer space.

426
00:35:44,075 --> 00:35:45,210
I am.

427
00:35:49,080 --> 00:35:50,248
Come on.

428
00:35:50,482 --> 00:35:51,750
There won't be four of us anyway.

429
00:35:54,119 --> 00:35:56,521
We won't have many opportunities
to drink together.

430
00:35:56,688 --> 00:35:57,756
Cheers.

431
00:36:00,659 --> 00:36:02,293
Why won't we have
many opportunities to drink?

432
00:36:05,030 --> 00:36:09,300
I was hoping to celebrate with you
after we find Ah Si.

433
00:36:10,101 --> 00:36:11,269
Celebrate for what?

434
00:36:11,670 --> 00:36:13,138
I'm going to work tomorrow.

435
00:36:16,908 --> 00:36:18,376
The graduation trip is over.

436
00:36:18,576 --> 00:36:19,944
It's time to do some work.

437
00:36:23,882 --> 00:36:24,916
That's right.

438
00:36:25,016 --> 00:36:26,651
The graduation trip is over.

439
00:36:27,886 --> 00:36:29,020
Cheers!

440
00:36:53,445 --> 00:36:55,346
You are not the "si"
in one, two, three, four.

441
00:36:55,413 --> 00:36:57,582
You are this "Si."

442
00:37:13,064 --> 00:37:15,767
You're called F4 in Yingde.

443
00:37:16,134 --> 00:37:17,602
Do you know what is F4?

444
00:37:18,203 --> 00:37:22,073
You're young dudes that are like brothers.

445
00:37:22,340 --> 00:37:24,008
Like four flowers.

446
00:37:25,443 --> 00:37:28,213
Everyone in our school knows you.

447
00:37:28,279 --> 00:37:31,416
I've been asking around. See.

448
00:37:31,783 --> 00:37:33,952
I got their phone numbers and addresses.

449
00:37:35,687 --> 00:37:36,821
I called them.

450
00:37:39,224 --> 00:37:40,859
I saw their missing person poster.

451
00:37:41,793 --> 00:37:43,361
What missing person poster?

452
00:37:43,495 --> 00:37:45,396
The electronic billboards on the streets.

453
00:37:47,465 --> 00:37:49,200
I called them and was scolded.

454
00:37:50,268 --> 00:37:51,536
Who are they?

455
00:37:52,504 --> 00:37:53,972
How could they scold people like that?

456
00:37:55,673 --> 00:37:57,308
They're looking for you
but are scolding you.

457
00:37:58,009 --> 00:37:59,778
Maybe they didn't know who you are.

458
00:38:00,078 --> 00:38:02,580
Even I wasn't myself,
they can't scold people like that.

459
00:38:08,653 --> 00:38:10,889
Maybe I shouldn't know who they are.

460
00:38:13,525 --> 00:38:19,464
Maybe I shouldn't know who I am.

461
00:38:20,298 --> 00:38:21,299
Ah Xing.

462
00:38:22,200 --> 00:38:24,602
Why does it seem
that everyone around me is bad?

463
00:38:26,938 --> 00:38:29,107
What kind of people was I?

464
00:38:30,108 --> 00:38:31,643
Who am I?

465
00:38:32,043 --> 00:38:33,077
What are you doing?

466
00:38:33,244 --> 00:38:35,613
What are you doing?
Tearing down the house?

467
00:38:35,780 --> 00:38:37,448
-Granny.
-See.

468
00:38:37,582 --> 00:38:39,984
I knew it. You won't help me water them.

469
00:38:40,285 --> 00:38:41,486
My flowers are dying of thirst.

470
00:38:41,686 --> 00:38:42,787
Let me help you.

471
00:38:42,854 --> 00:38:43,788
-Now?
-Okay.

472
00:38:43,855 --> 00:38:44,956
-Right now.
-Right now.

473
00:38:49,894 --> 00:38:51,462
You should change if you want to.

474
00:38:51,930 --> 00:38:53,264
Your past stays in the past.

475
00:38:53,798 --> 00:38:55,567
It's who you are now that matters.

476
00:38:56,901 --> 00:38:58,236
The most important thing is,

477
00:39:00,572 --> 00:39:02,373
remember paying your rent.

478
00:39:07,078 --> 00:39:08,613
-Go water them.
-Will do...

479
00:39:08,680 --> 00:39:10,715
If my babies die of thirst,

480
00:39:11,049 --> 00:39:13,785
-I'll come for you.
-Don't worry, Granny. I'm watering them.

481
00:39:24,963 --> 00:39:28,499
-What are you doing?
-Putting out your fire.

482
00:39:28,566 --> 00:39:30,635
You're the one that should be watered.
Why did you water me?

483
00:39:54,192 --> 00:39:55,193
You're laughing now.

484
00:39:55,293 --> 00:39:56,761
Are you happy now?

485
00:40:03,701 --> 00:40:05,036
-Out of water...
-You...

486
00:41:13,371 --> 00:41:14,305
Senior.

487
00:41:16,674 --> 00:41:17,809
Who are you?

488
00:41:18,309 --> 00:41:21,079
I'm doing a life interview
about the graduating seniors.

489
00:41:21,145 --> 00:41:22,914
I don't know if you're available now.

490
00:41:23,781 --> 00:41:24,983
Life interview?

491
00:41:26,317 --> 00:41:27,452
I don't think it's necessary.

492
00:41:27,585 --> 00:41:28,987
Please, senior.

493
00:41:29,053 --> 00:41:31,990
This will affect my sociology score
in the next semester.

494
00:41:32,156 --> 00:41:34,359
Please, senior.

495
00:41:38,529 --> 00:41:40,098
All right, get in the car.

496
00:42:01,352 --> 00:42:02,353
Thank you.

497
00:42:13,965 --> 00:42:16,034
I don't remember meeting you in Yingde?

498
00:42:16,567 --> 00:42:18,770
How could you remember
all the girls in Yingde?

499
00:42:20,004 --> 00:42:21,672
I remember all the beautiful ones.

500
00:42:22,473 --> 00:42:23,775
So I'm not beautiful enough?

501
00:42:26,044 --> 00:42:27,378
You are.

502
00:42:27,512 --> 00:42:29,547
You are beautiful and smart.

503
00:42:31,115 --> 00:42:33,584
I'm so happy
that I get praised by a senior.

504
00:42:35,286 --> 00:42:37,855
Right, have you started working?

505
00:42:38,022 --> 00:42:40,792
We want to know what you will do
after graduation.

506
00:42:41,526 --> 00:42:44,829
You must be working
in your family corporations, right?

507
00:42:46,964 --> 00:42:49,600
Speaking of it, Ximen is the first one
to settle down.

508
00:42:50,968 --> 00:42:53,037
Lei and I will start working soon.

509
00:42:57,341 --> 00:42:59,577
How about Daoming Si?

510
00:43:01,212 --> 00:43:03,014
He hasn't returned
from the graduation trip.

511
00:43:04,849 --> 00:43:07,085
Please don't get mad
at the question I'll ask you.

512
00:43:07,885 --> 00:43:08,719
Go ahead.

513
00:43:09,454 --> 00:43:12,723
Why are there rumors saying
that Daoming Si is in trouble?

514
00:43:14,325 --> 00:43:15,393
Are there?

515
00:43:15,860 --> 00:43:17,061
Who says that?

516
00:43:18,362 --> 00:43:20,431
The missing person posters
in the newspapers

517
00:43:20,498 --> 00:43:22,166
and the large billboard on the street.

518
00:43:27,738 --> 00:43:29,207
You must be very worried, right?

519
00:43:29,440 --> 00:43:30,808
You're so close.

520
00:43:33,644 --> 00:43:35,379
Isn't this a life interview?

521
00:43:35,446 --> 00:43:37,215
Why is it a soul interview now?

522
